                  </hi>. (<hi rend="italic">policeman, K</hi> 71). The prisoner was given into my charge at the Princess of Wales—I received these two shillings from Mr. Sims, in presence of Mr. Callaghan—the shillings are both marked, but differently.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18520614-name-130" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18520614-name-130" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18520614-name-130" type="surname" value="WEBSTER"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18520614-name-130" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM WEBSTER</persName>
                  </hi>. These two shillings uttered by the prisoner are bad, and from the same mould—this one uttered by the other man is also bad.</p>
